WEBVTT

00:00.760 --> 00:01.480
Why not

00:02.680 --> 00:03.760
Split this pastry

00:05.680 --> 00:06.360
Half for each

00:08.320 --> 00:09.320
You're right

00:09.920 --> 00:11.560
Just like when you were children

00:12.120 --> 00:13.320
Half for each

00:16.480 --> 00:17.040
This way

00:17.040 --> 00:18.560
No one is shortchanged

00:24.040 --> 00:25.360
I'll make more later

00:25.480 --> 00:26.680
And send them to you

00:28.880 --> 00:30.120
Thank you, Mother
